    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You have to see this absolute gem! It\u2019s in gorgeous, mint condition and has been pampered since day one. Seriously, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot\u2014spotless inside and out! I\u2019ve loved every mile in it, but it\u2019s time for a new home. If you're looking for something that\u2019s been treated with a ton of love and is ready to hit the road today, this is the one for you! \u2728",
