    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E46 M3, a true driver\u2019s specimen maintained to a fastidious standard. At its heart lies the S54B32 inline-six, featuring a fully serviced VANOS system and recent valve adjustments for optimal timing and top-end performance. The chassis integrity is guaranteed by proactive rear subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension featuring OEM bushings and Bilstein dampers. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring the balanced handling dynamics this platform is renowned for. This is a turn-key, investment-grade machine with zero deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
