    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a true time-capsule vehicle. Finished in its original factory deep-gloss metallic paint, the exterior is absolutely flawless, having been protected by a professional ceramic coating and stored in a climate-controlled environment since day one. There are no stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found. Inside, the cabin retains its original showroom fragrance, with the premium leather upholstery showing zero signs of bolster wear, fading, or creasing. Every electronic feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver assistance suite, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Under the hood, the engine bay is immaculate, reflecting a meticulous service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. The vehicle drives with the tightness and precision of a brand-new car, with no rattles, vibrations, or mechanical imperfections. Included are all original keys, the original window sticker, and a comprehensive binder of maintenance records. This is a pristine example suited for the most discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
